<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q29_v2" title="Q29 Variante 2" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En un complejo deportivo se cobra un precio proporcional al tiempo de uso de una cancha. Algunos valores se presentan en el siguiente registro:</p>
    <div>
      <m:math display="block">
        <m:mtable>
          <m:mtr>
            <m:mtd><m:mtext>Tiempo (minutos)</m:mtext></m:mtd>
            <m:mtd><m:mtext>Precio (pesos)</m:mtext></m:mtd>
          </m:mtr>
          <m:mtr>
            <m:mtd><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mtd>
            <m:mtd><m:mn>3000</m:mn></m:mtd>
          </m:mtr>
          <m:mtr>
            <m:mtd><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:mtd>
            <m:mtd><m:mn>6000</m:mn></m:mtd>
          </m:mtr>
          <m:mtr>
            <m:mtd><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mtd>
            <m:mtd><m:mn>9000</m:mn></m:mtd>
          </m:mtr>
          <m:mtr>
            <m:mtd><m:mn>40</m:mn></m:mtd>
            <m:mtd><m:mn>12000</m:mn></m:mtd>
          </m:mtr>
        </m:mtable>
      </m:math>
    </div>
    <p>Si <m:math><m:mi>P</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:math> representa el precio en pesos por <m:math><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:math> minutos de arriendo, 
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    ¿cuál de las siguientes expresiones es consistente con la información del registro?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mi>P</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9000</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mi>t</m:mi>
        </m:math>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mi>P</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mi>t</m:mi>
        </m:math>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mi>P</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>9000</m:mn>
        </m:math>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mi>P</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mi>t</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>9000</m:mn>
        </m:math>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
  </qti-item-body>
